cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Collapse3, please cite it as below."
title: "Collapse3: measuring competence vs. performance with an exact game oracle"
abstract: >-
  A perfect-information, deterministic 3x3x3 gravity-and-removal game small
  enough to solve exactly, used as an oracle to measure agent competence as
  value-based regret independent of any opponent distribution.
authors:
  - family-names: McCormack
    given-names: Rob
